{
  "name": "IconCriterion",
  "summary": "<p>图标集条件格式的所有条件均包含在 <strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/IconCriteria/IconCriteria .htm#IconCriteria.IconCriteria\">IconCriteria</a></strong> 集合中。通过将索引传递到集合中，您可以访问集合中的每个 <strong>IconCriterion</strong> 对象。有关详细信息，请参阅示例。</p>\n<p><b class=\"mainheaders\">示例</b></p><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例创建了一个代表测试分数的数字范围，然后对该范围应用了图标集条件格式规则。图标集的类型将从默认图标变为五箭头图标集。最后，将阈值类型从百分点修改为硬编码数字。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-comment\">// Fill cells with sample data</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;C1&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Value2</span> = <span class=\"hljs-number\">55</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;C2&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Value2</span> = <span class=\"hljs-number\">92</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;C3&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Value2</span> = <span class=\"hljs-number\">88</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;C4&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Value2</span> = <span class=\"hljs-number\">77</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;C5&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Value2</span> = <span class=\"hljs-number\">66</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;C6&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Value2</span> = <span class=\"hljs-number\">93</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;C7&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Value2</span> = <span class=\"hljs-number\">76</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;C8&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Value2</span> = <span class=\"hljs-number\">80</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;C9&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Value2</span> = <span class=\"hljs-number\">79</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;C10&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Value2</span> = <span class=\"hljs-number\">83</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;C11&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Value2</span> = <span class=\"hljs-number\">66</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;C12&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Value2</span> = <span class=\"hljs-number\">74</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;C1:C12&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Select</span>()\n\n    <span class=\"hljs-comment\">// Create an icon set conditional format for the created sample data range</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> iconSet = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Selection</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">FormatConditions</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">AddIconSetCondition</span>()\n\n    <span class=\"hljs-comment\">// Change the icon set to a five-arrow icon set</span>\n    iconSet.<span class=\"hljs-property\">IconSet</span> = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveWorkbook</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">IconSets</span>(xl5Arrows)\n\n    <span class=\"hljs-comment\">// The IconCriterion collection contains all IconCriteria</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-comment\">// By indexing into the collection you can modify each criterion</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> iconCriteria1 = iconSet.<span class=\"hljs-property\">IconCriteria</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>)\n    iconCriteria1.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Type</span> = xlConditionValueNumber\n    iconCriteria1.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Value</span> = <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>\n    iconCriteria1.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Operator</span> = <span class=\"hljs-number\">7</span>\n\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> iconCriteria2 = iconSet.<span class=\"hljs-property\">IconCriteria</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>)\n    iconCriteria2.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Type</span> = xlConditionValueNumber\n    iconCriteria2.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Value</span> = <span class=\"hljs-number\">60</span>\n    iconCriteria2.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Operator</span> = <span class=\"hljs-number\">7</span>\n\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> iconCriteria3 = iconSet.<span class=\"hljs-property\">IconCriteria</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">3</span>)\n    iconCriteria3.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Type</span> = xlConditionValueNumber\n    iconCriteria3.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Value</span> = <span class=\"hljs-number\">70</span>\n    iconCriteria3.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Operator</span> = <span class=\"hljs-number\">7</span>\n\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> iconCriteria4 = iconSet.<span class=\"hljs-property\">IconCriteria</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">4</span>)\n    iconCriteria4.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Type</span> = xlConditionValueNumber\n    iconCriteria4.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Value</span> = <span class=\"hljs-number\">80</span>\n    iconCriteria4.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Operator</span> = <span class=\"hljs-number\">7</span>\n\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> iconCriteria5 = iconSet.<span class=\"hljs-property\">IconCriteria</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">5</span>)\n    iconCriteria5.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Type</span> = xlConditionValueNumber\n    iconCriteria5.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Value</span> = <span class=\"hljs-number\">90</span>\n    iconCriteria5.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Operator</span> = <span class=\"hljs-number\">7</span>\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例将第一张工作表上区域 A1:A10 中第一个图标集条件格式的第二个图标的类型设置为xlConditionValueNumber，并将该图标的阈值设置为30。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> iconSet = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;A1:A10&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">FormatConditions</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>)\n    iconSet.<span class=\"hljs-property\">IconCriteria</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Type</span> = xlConditionValueNumber\n    iconSet.<span class=\"hljs-property\">IconCriteria</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Value</span> = <span class=\"hljs-number\">30</span>\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
  "description": "<p>代表图标集中单个图标的条件。此条件指定了值的范围以及与图标集条件格式规则中的图标关联的阈值类型。</p>\n",
  "category": "et",
  "properties": [
    {
      "name": "Icon",
      "summary": "<p>设置图标集条件格式规则中图标条件的 <strong>Icon</strong> 属性后，<strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/IconSetCondition/IconSetCondition .htm#IconSetCondition.IconSet\">IconSet</a></strong> 属性更改为 <strong>xlCustomSet</strong>。</p>\n",
      "description": "<p>返回或指定图标集条件格式规则中某个条件的图标。可读/写。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例创建一个图标集条件格式规则，该规则在指定百分比中显示四个图标。图标集最初设置为使用“四向箭头(彩色)”图标集，但是 Icon 属性用来重写用于第一和第三条件的图标。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-comment\">// 第一个条件的图标是“红十字”图标，第二个条件的图标是“4 个箭头 (彩色)”图标集的第二个箭头，第三个条件的图标是“黄色交通灯”图标，第四个条件的图标是“4 个箭头 (彩色)”图标集的第四个箭头。</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;B1:B10&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Select</span>()\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Selection</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">FormatConditions</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">AddIconSetCondition</span>()\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Selection</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">FormatConditions</span>(<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Selection</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">FormatConditions</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Count</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">SetFirstPriority</span>()\n\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> formatCondition = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Selection</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">FormatConditions</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>)\n    formatCondition.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ReverseOrder</span> = <span class=\"hljs-literal\">false</span>\n    formatCondition.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ShowIconOnly</span> = <span class=\"hljs-literal\">false</span>\n    formatCondition.<span class=\"hljs-property\">IconSet</span> = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveWorkbook</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">IconSets</span>(xl4Arrows)\n\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> iconCriterion1 = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Selection</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">FormatConditions</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">IconCriteria</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>)\n    iconCriterion1.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Icon</span> = xlIconRedCross\n\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> iconCriterion2 = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Selection</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">FormatConditions</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">IconCriteria</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>)\n    iconCriterion2.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Type</span> = xlConditionValuePercent\n    iconCriterion2.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Value</span> = <span class=\"hljs-number\">25</span>\n    iconCriterion2.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Operator</span> = <span class=\"hljs-number\">7</span>\n\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> iconCriterion3 = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Selection</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">FormatConditions</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">IconCriteria</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">3</span>)\n    iconCriterion3.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Type</span> = xlConditionValuePercent\n    iconCriterion3.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Value</span> = <span class=\"hljs-number\">50</span>\n    iconCriterion3.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Operator</span> = <span class=\"hljs-number\">7</span>\n    iconCriterion3.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Icon</span> = xlIconYellowTrafficLight\n\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> iconCriterion4 = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Selection</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">FormatConditions</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">IconCriteria</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">4</span>)\n    iconCriterion4.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Type</span> = xlConditionValuePercent\n    iconCriterion4.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Value</span> = <span class=\"hljs-number\">75</span>\n    iconCriterion4.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Operator</span> = <span class=\"hljs-number\">7</span>\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例将活动工作表上区域 A1:A10 中第一个图标集条件格式的第二个图标设置为xlIconYellowExclamation。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> iconSet = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;A1:A10&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">FormatConditions</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>)\n    iconSet.<span class=\"hljs-property\">IconCriteria</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Icon</span> = xlIconYellowExclamation\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "XlIcon",
      "readonly": false
    },
    {
      "name": "Index",
      "summary": "<p>对于图标集，此属性将为最小阈值返回值“1”，为下一个阈值返回值“2”，依此类推。</p>\n",
      "description": "<p>返回一个 <strong>Long</strong> 值，该值表示条件代表的阈值。只读。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示活动工作表上区域 A1:A10 中第一个图标集条件格式的第二个图标的阈值。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> iconSet = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;A1:A10&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">FormatConditions</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(iconSet.<span class=\"hljs-property\">IconCriteria</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Index</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例将第一张工作表上区域 A1:A10 中第一个图标集条件格式的所有图标的阈值赋值给活动工作表的单元格。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> iconSet = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;A1:A10&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">FormatConditions</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">for</span> (<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> i = <span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>; i &lt;= iconSet.<span class=\"hljs-property\">IconCriteria</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Count</span>; i++) {\n        <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Cells</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(i, <span class=\"hljs-number\">3</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Value2</span> = iconSet.<span class=\"hljs-property\">IconCriteria</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(i).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Index</span>\n    }\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "number（int4 精度）",
      "readonly": true
    },
    {
      "name": "Operator",
      "summary": "<p>对于图标集条件格式规则，此属性只能设置为以下两个常量之一：<strong>xlGreater</strong> 或 <strong>xlGreaterEqual</strong>。</p>\n",
      "description": "<p>返回或设置 <strong><a href=\"topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/枚举/XlFormatConditionOperator 枚举.html\">XlFormatConditionOperator</a></strong> 枚举的常量之一，该常量指定阈值是“大于”还是“大于或等于”该阈值。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示活动工作表上区域 A1:A10 中第一个图标集条件格式的第一个图标的运算符是否为xlGreaterEqual。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> iconSet = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;A1:A10&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">FormatConditions</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(iconSet.<span class=\"hljs-property\">IconCriteria</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Operator</span> == xlGreaterEqual)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例将第一张工作表上区域 A1:A10 中第一个图标集条件格式的第三个图标的运算符设置为xlGreater。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> iconSet = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;A1:A10&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">FormatConditions</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>)\n    iconSet.<span class=\"hljs-property\">IconCriteria</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">3</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Operator</span> = xlGreater\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "number（int4 精度）",
      "readonly": false
    },
    {
      "name": "Type",
      "summary": "<p>图标集的阈值类型可以是数字、百分比、公式或百分点值。如果将类型设置为百分点值，将使用 ET 中的 Percentile 函数确定阈值。</p>\n",
      "description": "<p>返回或设置 <strong><a href=\"topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/枚举/XlConditionValueTypes 枚举.html\">XlConditionValueTypes</a></strong> 枚举的常量之一，该常量指定如何确定图标集的阈值。可读写。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示第一张工作表上区域 A1:A10 中第一个图标集条件格式的第一个图标的类型是否为xlConditionValuePercent。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> iconSet = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;A1:A10&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">FormatConditions</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(iconSet.<span class=\"hljs-property\">IconCriteria</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Type</span> == xlConditionValuePercent)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例将活动工作表上区域 A1:A10 中第一个图标集条件格式的第二个图标的类型设置为xlConditionValueNumber。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> iconSet = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;A1:A10&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">FormatConditions</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>)\n    iconSet.<span class=\"hljs-property\">IconCriteria</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Type</span> = xlConditionValueNumber\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "XlConditionValueTypes",
      "readonly": false
    },
    {
      "name": "Value",
      "summary": "<p>仅当条件格式的 <strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/IconCriterion/IconCriterion .htm#IconCriterion.Type\">IconCriterion.Type</a></strong> 属性设置为常量 <strong>xlConditionValueNumber</strong>、<strong>xlConditionValuePercent</strong>、<strong>xlConditionValuePercentile</strong> 或 <strong>xlConditionValueFormula</strong> 时，才能设置该值。</p>\n<p>如果阈值类型为公式，则可以将公式设置为 <strong>String</strong> 类型。而公式必须返回单个数字。</p>\n",
      "description": "<p>返回或设置条件格式中图标的阈值。可读/写 <strong>Variant</strong> 类型。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例判断如果活动工作表上区域 A1:A10 中第一个图标集条件格式的第二个图标的类型为xlConditionValuePercent，则显示该图标的阈值。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> iconSet = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;A1:A10&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">FormatConditions</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> iconCriterion = iconSet.<span class=\"hljs-property\">IconCriteria</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span> (iconCriterion.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Type</span> == xlConditionValuePercent) {\n        <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(iconCriterion.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Value</span>)\n    }\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例将第一张工作表上区域 A1:A10 中第一个图标集条件格式的第三个图标的阈值设置为60。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> iconSet = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;A1:A10&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">FormatConditions</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>)\n    iconSet.<span class=\"hljs-property\">IconCriteria</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">3</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Value</span> = <span class=\"hljs-number\">60</span>\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "any",
      "readonly": false
    }
  ],
  "functions": []
}